Small module for Lighttpd created in C with memcache module,
main purpose was to block streaming video files for unathorized IP addresses


In lighttpd config 

module name "mod_protect_download"
Helper script premissions need to be 0644 and execute

ALSO need to have this options
protect-download.server-ip = ' '
protect-download.server-port = ' '
protect-download.deny-url  = ' ' 
protect-download.debug = 'enable'
